### ⚡ D. Performance & UX

| # | Suggestion | Effort |
|---|-----------|--------|
| 14 | **Add auto-refresh** — Poll for match updates every 30-60 seconds on the home page, or implement WebSockets for live scores | Medium |
| 15 | **Add `react-query` or `SWR`** — Replace manual `useState` + `useEffect` data fetching with a caching library for better UX (stale-while-revalidate, automatic retry, dedup) | Medium |
