| 17 | **Lazy-load admin components** — Use `React.lazy()` for [AdminPage](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/client/src/pages/AdminPage.jsx#354-569), `CanvasExporter`, [BracketTree](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/client/src/components/BracketTree.jsx#102-222) to reduce initial bundle size | Low |
| 18 | **Add SEO meta tags dynamically** — The [index.html](file:///d:/Ramadan-matchs/client/index.html) has static meta; consider updating `<title>` per page (e.g., "ربع النهائي — دوري رمضان") | Low |

